This is a help document for my program icode

It is a shell application, that can create shell scripts being able to 
make them executable while aiding the user in shell programming 

to run your named bash script you can open a new shell by selecting option 3 
and that will open a new shell window where the user can type ./filename.bash
to execute the script 

option 4 will allow you to continue working on your script

you call make a bash script executable from this application 
you can also open a new shell window and continue working on the script at 
any time 

scroll upwards

